ObjectClass.Name: Octo (Progen)
ObjectClass.Description:
Must be near a Sepi or Pharo that is also in Progeneration mode
Must be near a Spyre to progenerate aerospace units.

Objective.Name: Cancel Progen for All
Objective.Details: Cancel out of progeneretaion for\this and surrounding progen units

Objective.Name: Repeat Last Order
Objective.Details: \Repeats the last production order,\not including RP dispatch

Objective.Name: Set to Idle
Objective.Details: \Clear smart-production memory

Objective.Name: Set Congregation Pointers
Objective.Details: \Set congregation point and/or\hierarchy leader for pregenerated units

Objective.Name: Clear Congregation Pointers
Objective.Details: \Clear congregation point and\hierarchy leader

Objective.Name: Produce Octo
Objective.Details: Biological melee assault trooper\Effective against ground targets\Good at absorbing enemy fire\Morphs into R.P or Dome\Invisible in Fog of War

Objective.Name: Produce Squiddy/Sepi
Objective.Details: Biological support shock trooper\High damage against air and ground units\Cloaks while moving\Morphs into Mound or Reaph\Invisible in Fog of War

Objective.Name: Produce Pharo
Objective.Details: Biological armored shock grenadier\Slow close-range splash anti-ground brawler\Cloak detector\Morphs into Spyre or Arcticus\Invisible in Fog of War

Objective.Name: Produce Octopod
Objective.Details: Biological main ground-assault armor\Mobile anti-ground heavy sniper\Progenerates advanced units\Morphs into Ghost

Objective.Name: Produce Humbolt/Sepipod
Objective.Details: Tactical air superiority fighter-bomber\Good scout and raider; Biological\Progenerates adv. octo and pharo units\Detects cloaked units\Can Chronobomb (Specials research)

Objective.Name: Produce Vampire/Pharopod
Objective.Details: Biological steatlh strike-bomber\Very high damage against ground targets\Progenerates adv. octo and sepi units\Self-Cloaks; Mists to avoid death

Objective.Name: Octo
Objective.Details: \Must have a progenerating\Sepi and Pharo pair

Objective.Name: Squiddy/Sepi
Objective.Details: \Must have a progenerating\Pharo and Octo pair

Objective.Name: Pharo
Objective.Details: \Must have a progenerating\Octo and Sepi pair

Objective.Name: Octopod
Objective.Details: \Must have a progenerating\Sepi and Pharo pair

Objective.Name: Humbolt/Sepipod
Objective.Details: \Must have a progenerating\Pharo and Octo pair\Must be near a Spyre

Objective.Name: Vampire/Pharopod
Objective.Details: \Must have a progenerating\Octo and Sepi pair\Must be near a Spyre

Objective.Name: Octo Resource Processor
Objective.Details: - place near resource bins\Assimilates resources: Power and Q-Plasma\Can bootstrap and convert Q-P into L-C\Can move itself
